> # Badge
> ## (Default: Off)
> - - -
> * **Off:**  
>     No badge will be shown.
>
> * **On:**  
>     If the app is currently loaded, a badge will be displayed on the app's icon on the home screen (SpringBoard).
> 
>     The badge will be displayed regardless of backgrounding method/state.

- - -

> # Status Bar Icon
> ## (Default: Off)
> ### "Backgrounder" method only
> - - -
> * **Off:**  
>     No status bar icon will be shown.
>
> * **On:**  
>     If the app has backgrounding enabled, an icon will be displayed in the status bar when the app is the current app.
>
>     In other words, the presence of this icon indicates that the current app will continue to run in the background when minimized. 
